name: NewYearWishes
0:
”Alexa, open new year wish”
”Alexa, launch new year wish”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: new year wish
des: Ring in the New Year with firecrackers, confetti, champagne and happy New Year wishes! The New Year brings with it a fresh start, new opportunities and an exhilarating sense of rejuvenation. We often make New Year’s resolutions in an attempt to improve ourselves and to be better towards others. Expressing our love, gratitude, respect and appreciation to others on this day. Just say “Alexa, open new year wish” and Alexa wish you happy New Year wishes!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
